description:
In this festive karaoke video, we take you on a journey to "Go, tell it on the mountain" with lyrics. Sing your heart out with us as we celebrate the holidays with this popular X'mas song!

If you're looking for a fun way to celebrate the holidays, then this karaoke video is for you! We'll take you on a journey to one of your favorite Christmas songs, "Go, tell it on the mountain" with lyrics. Sing along with us as we have a blast celebrating the holiday season!

Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters  youtube production!
